{"tid":312883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港前途女童被捲入七人車底亡","createTime":"2017-07-07T23:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T23:39:00.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d326b88ae8670cb7d4d7f982d26ed796d03f7787","tid":312883,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T23:33:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170707/56928094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170707%2F56928094&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9e5b79e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170707%2F56928094&h=85074496\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170707/56928094</a><br />\n<br />\n我指個女童似香港前途<br />\n中港車等如強國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佐敦晚上發生恐怖車禍！事發在晚上約8時50分，一名年約3歲的尼泊爾女童於佐敦文蔚街近渡船街過路時，遭一部掛中港牌的白色七人車撞到並捲入車底拖行。警方及消防接報到場救援，消防需要用車唧將七人車唧起，終將女童救出送院搶救。<br />\n現場消息指，涉事白色七人車把女童撞到並捲入車底後，一直繼續前行，其間把小童拖行約200米，直至文成街與文匯街交界時，司機才由途人喝止，知道發生車禍，連忙停車。<br />\n現場遺下一條長長的血路，血迹中還夾雜着頭髮絲。事發後警員在場調查，受傷女童的父親帶着另一名男童，神情哀傷；而涉事司機則在警車上協助警方調查。"},{"pid":"1932711ced653f12dddf07c9e5e2451664443428","tid":312883,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T23:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942f5a1ba30bb5b35754ff2341b76279675aadeb","tid":312883,"uid":67501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T23:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/073857_e9fe6159d3fbfac21b48b3197298a0b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F073857_e9fe6159d3fbfac21b48b3197298a0b3.jpg&h=193774a7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}